video.title: Money Heist
video.synopsis: Eight thieves take hostages and lock themselves in the Royal Mint of Spain as a criminal mastermind manipulates the police to carry out his plan.

episodes.synopsis: The Professor recruits a young female robber and seven other criminals for a grand heist, targeting the Royal Mint of Spain.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Hostage negotiator Raquel makes initial contact with the Professor. One of the hostages is a crucial part of the thieves' plans.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Police grab an image of the face of one of the robbers. Raquel is suspicious of the gentleman she meets at a bar.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Raquel suffers a personal crisis with her ex. The hostages are frightened by the gunshots they overheard. The thieves argue among themselves.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: The thieves let a medical team enter the Mint, and an undercover policeman sneaks in with them. Can the Professor stay one step ahead of Raquel?
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Mónica's condition worsens. The Professor enjoys the spoils of his latest trick. Río is disturbed by news he sees on the television.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: A break in the investigation and a mistake by one of the thieves puts the Professor at serious risk of being discovered.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Tokyo catches Alison chatting with Río and confronts her. The police suspect a spy is in their midst.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: The Professor races to stop a witness from identifying him. Berlín seeks revenge once his own name is revealed and slandered in the press.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Raquel enters the Mint to ascertain that all of the hostages are still alive and well. Nairobi gives Alison advice.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Ángel and Raquel question each other's loyalties. Mónica makes a move on Denver. Río is faced with a difficult decision.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Arturo continues to formulate an escape plan for a group of hostages. The Professor reveals who gave him the idea for the heist.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: The Professor meets Raquel's mother under stressful circumstances. At the Mint, the thieves offer the hostages a decision: money or freedom?
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: As forensic experts comb the Toledo country house for DNA,  the Professor loses control. Inside the Mint, the robbers' nerves reach a breaking point.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: The police interrogate the first robber to be captured. Furious over Berlín's recent actions, Río takes a stand against him.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Hoping to learn the Professor's identity, Raquel appeals to her captive's emotions. A punishment for "high treason" sparks a revolt among the robbers.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Recognizing their plan isn't working out, the robbers instead aim to win over the public via the press. Raquel plots a trap to capture the Professor.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Arturo tries to set another escape plan in motion. During a conversation with Salva, Raquel spots a tiny detail that gets her mind racing.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: After confessing a long-held secret, Moscow loses his son's trust. A contingency plan to free Tokyo hits a snag, forcing her to improvise.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: With one of their own critically injured, the robbers race against time to save his life. During a moment alone, Ariadna makes a confession to Mónica.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: After being removed from the case due to her relationship with the Professor, Raquel sets out to conduct her own search for the mastermind.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: As the police enter the Mint, Berlín leads the robbers in a final showdown. Will they escape with the 984 million euros -- and with their lives intact?
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: When Río is captured, a distraught Tokyo turns to the Professor for help. Armed with a bold new plan, they reunite the team in order to rescue him.
episodes.title: We're Back

episodes.synopsis: The Professor recruits Martín to put his brother's plan into action and target the Bank of Spain. First step? Create total chaos.
episodes.title: Aikido

episodes.synopsis: Tokyo and Nairobi's efforts go drastically awry. The Professor recalls Berlín detailing how they'd steal the gold from the water-logged vault.
episodes.title: 48 Meters Underground

episodes.synopsis: Tamayo's breaches of protocol surprise the Professor. Bogotá calms Denver's anxieties. With time running out, Palermo initiates the "Flipper" plan.
episodes.title: It's Dolphin Time

episodes.synopsis: The Professor shocks officials with his latest stunt, but in response, a new inspector rattles Raquel. Palermo and Nairobi get into a heated argument.
episodes.title: Boom, Boom, Ciao

episodes.synopsis: Just as Inspector Sierra orchestrates a plan to sneak a team into the Bank of Spain, the Professor and Raquel lose communication with Palermo.
episodes.title: Everything Seemed Insignificant

episodes.synopsis: Tokyo's happiness turns bittersweet. Ángel closes in on a quarreling Raquel and the Professor. Authorities offer a multimillion-dollar reward for tips.
episodes.title: A Quick Vacation

episodes.synopsis: Tokyo attempts to drown her sorrows. Sierra uses personal tactics to target a vulnerable Nairobi, while Suárez continues to hunt down Raquel.
episodes.title: Astray

episodes.synopsis: Anger and grief heighten tensions between the group. The Professor, while in mourning, attempts to make a daring and dangerous escape.
episodes.title: Game Over

episodes.synopsis: Palermo shocks the group with his actions. Sierra pressures her subject to take a deal. The Professor remembers his brother's wedding.
episodes.title: Berlin's Wedding

episodes.synopsis: The Professor's mole attempts to pass along his message to the person inside the tent. Denver's jealousy toward Mónica and Rio's friendship heightens.
episodes.title: Anatomy Lesson

episodes.synopsis: In the past, Berlin predicts that Gandía will cause problems for the operation. Sierra's interrogation of Lisbon leads to a personal revelation.
episodes.title: Pasodoble

episodes.synopsis: Denver turns to an undercover source for help. Nairobi attempts to motivate her team as the danger around them intensifies.
episodes.title: 5 Minutes Earlier

episodes.synopsis: With Nairobi held hostage, Gandía negotiates with the crew. The Professor desperately seeks a new plan to save his team.
episodes.title: TKO

episodes.synopsis: The group reels following the attack on one of their own. The Professor puts his adjusted plan in motion with the help of new recruits and Palermo.
episodes.title: Strike the Tent

episodes.synopsis: The Professor, Benjamin and the others attempt to free Lisbon. Tokyo's anger threatens her faith in the plan. Sierra takes matters into her own hands.
episodes.title: The Paris Plan

episodes.synopsis: The Professor faces off with Sierra as Tamayo raises the stakes of the negotiations by calling the army. In the past, Berlin meets with a family member.
episodes.title: The End of the Road

episodes.synopsis: Arturo seizes an opportunity to fight back while escalating a personal vengeance. Lisbon makes a crucial discovery.
episodes.title: Do You Believe in Reincarnation?

episodes.synopsis: A betrayal and an emergency both catch Sierra by surprise. Palermo rallies the troops as the army closes in on the gang.
episodes.title: Welcome to the Spectacle of Life

episodes.synopsis: With Helsinki's life in danger, the thieves mount a covert counter attack. Years earlier, Berlin and his son conduct their first heist together.
episodes.title: Your Place in Heaven

episodes.synopsis: While surrounded by gunfire and trapped in the kitchen, Tokyo reminisces about her first love and her initial encounter with the Professor.
episodes.title: Live Many Lives

episodes.synopsis: Sierra takes advantage of the Professor's grief and gains the upper hand. Meanwhile, the team deals with the emotional fallout of their dead friend.
episodes.title: Escape Valve

episodes.synopsis: Tamayo mounts a manhunt in his neighborhood as his foes hide. In the past, Berlin and Palermo explain how they plan on getting the gold out of the bank.
episodes.title: Wishful Thinking

episodes.synopsis: Tamayo hunts for the gold as the team races against the clock. Mónica worries she's having a psychotic break. Years earlier, Berlin is deceived.
episodes.title: The Elegance Theory

episodes.synopsis: The Professor is left reeling after his tactics are used against him, and when it seems like all hope is lost, he makes a bold decision.
episodes.title: Pillow Talk

episodes.synopsis: With multiple lives on the line and Spain's economy at stake, the Professor and Tamayo engage in one final showdown.
episodes.title: A Family Tradition
